{"tid":185890,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"試過大家食既人入一入黎 （無圖）","createTime":"2017-04-03T18:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T00:54:42.000Z","uid":95837,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbde4aa5a258589fb45be2c457c0c2c1358d5473","tid":185890,"uid":95837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:57:21.000Z","msg":"之前比高登仔係咁吹奏既大家食今日終於試到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Es4P2V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Es4P2V.jpg&h=1161d253&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/023508_c4890d57739f81b32ffb4ef828948888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F023508_c4890d57739f81b32ffb4ef828948888.jpg&h=26296708&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0A33CW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0A33CW.jpg&h=18fd158f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4hqS2t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4hqS2t.jpg&h=f7f322cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無左金槍人local既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔緊要 我諗啲品質都應該唔差得去邊<br />\n啲款式又多 平民黎講都算可以<br />\n夜晚8點開始冇咩人 反而隔離個間車仔麵啲人仲排緊隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫左個青瓜 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9HaA9O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9HaA9O.jpg&h=fb12b3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n還好啦個青瓜 但係唔知係咪因為我個人重口味 碟野完全無味既 感覺上仲有啲 鞋 口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vv5761V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVv5761V.jpg&h=d253548e&s={SIZE}\" />到個煎餃子，基本上同八方雲集一撚樣，但就油過我塊面囉，心諗唉一餐半餐算鳩數，最多做翻多啲運動補數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後尾打大佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/025037_55e07b3d18905577aa4928c4b4642f46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F025037_55e07b3d18905577aa4928c4b4642f46.jpg&h=b20640b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個飯唔可以話好食 <br />\n而且個賣相就差到爆<br />\n呢張相係佢上枱影既我無郁過<br />\n心諗比碟狗飯我食做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後尾我肚餓關係食曬啲野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n埋單成7十幾蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32HJc92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32HJc92.jpg&h=980e904c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比完錢我心諗 頭先食左啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35aaf7a1a984fd8da2b16071cacd2721dddb12c5","tid":185890,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:58:02.000Z","msg":"去撚錯啦柒頭"},{"pid":"e623784687466a8ad2fc80ab2098e64a5d929c90","tid":185890,"uid":64143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWfO0C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWfO0C.png&h=87e4e240&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed676628091d77e05e7f71ad1642d41079ba0618","tid":185890,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:59:04.000Z","msg":"呢間假架 on9<br />\n<br />\n真果間叫大家食J"},{"pid":"ca339d6b89d6f883b0cdfa046c083d5fde81442d","tid":185890,"uid":95837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:05:19.000Z","msg":"屌囉 唔怪之得咁撚難食 完來